node.text: @your_fabulous_brand Thank you, Georgina! ✨ Writing on IG and on paper helps me sort out my thoughts!
@positiveleepeilin yes! The power of writing! 🌈

🌧️We're in the same storm, but we're not in the same boat 🌊⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
Some of us are in a fairly cosy boat with our loved ones 🚤 Some are alone in tiny sampans and ricochetting amongst the huge waves 🛶 Some are in luxury yachts with sun beds to enjoy the view ⛴️ Some are in crowded makeshift boats without individual beds 🚢Some are in lifeboats, trying to pull in people who have fallen into the water 🚣🏻‍♀️👩🏻‍⚕️🏥⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
😔If you're feeling worried, stressed or anxious because of the waves that beat non-stop upon your boat, there's professional help who's here to listen at 1800-202-6868 (National CARE Hotline) 📞⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
🇸🇬Also, every Thursday at 8pm till CB ends, landmarks around the world and in Singapore, such as MBS, Gardens by the Bay and the Esplanade are lit up in blue as a sign of solidarity against Covid-19 and all the challenges it brings 💙⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
This situation affects all of us differently. Let's float closer, so we can weather it together 🤝 This storm WILL pass and we can celebrate the rainbows face-to-face after.⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
Sending you my love 💙⁠
.
✨🤝Please share this information with anyone who you think could use a professional listening ear 👂🏻✨

.⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
#SeeItBlue #MakeItBlue⁠ #StayHomeforSG #ItsOkayNotToBeOkay #MentalWellness #SGUnited #CircuitBreakerSG #CBLife #CircuitBreaker
@acultivatedliving Been thinking a lot about this situation and somehow the metaphor of boats is simple and has stuck. Stay happy! 😘
"Let's float closer, so we can weather it together." I love this - and love how despite everything, this is bringing people closer together. Stay well!
@raiseyourwordsdesign Hi Elisabeth! I’m learning so much more about underserved groups during this time... and I actually talk more with my mum on Skype than f2f! 😂
Such a great message! Thanks for sharing resources to support those who need it.
@juststaceyj Yeah, it’s easier to just assume we’re all alike with the same strengths and struggles. Our boats are all different though! 🛶🚤🛳
I have loved seeing this message. I love that people are realizing that our struggles are different. That our lives are different. Be well and be safe.
@fj.mama Our landmarks are so pretty huh! So proud of our country ✨💙✨
Interesting!!!! #letsdoittogether
@freshpages.co 😘 The social differences have been twisting and turning in my mind, and finally turned into this analogy, which helps me grapple this situation better. Visual person here! 🙋🏻‍♀️😝
I love this analogy. It fits so well!
@miahere_miathere Just keep swimming, just keep swimming
Keep your ahead afloat!!
@brooke_hall_ All the best with your sessions next week, Brooke! 💪🏻
Thanks for sharing this information!
@brookekanitz Omigosh, Brooke, you’re a nurse AND with 4 boys. Ultimate RESPECT!!! 🙌🏻
@brookekanitz How are you this season, Brooke??
Yessss...all different journeys!
@tentaclesandtea.nicole ✨Nicole!!! You definitely are my girl!!! I’ll do it!!! Thanks for the nudge! 😍
@positiveleepeilin 🤗
Such a good message. (Unrelated, did you see the #Halfway2Halloween posts? I feel like you would have a great one!)
@your_fabulous_brand Thank you, Georgina! ✨ Writing on IG and on paper helps me sort out my thoughts!
@positiveleepeilin yes! The power of writing! 🌈
Love your words!
